{"tid":1524530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［901入機場］黑警恐襲！唔使講野，入機場哂冷","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:23:56.000Z","uid":159507,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"93503e6fa2be0ab90430ba569c007d6b9c2dd864","tid":1524530,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:28:48.000Z","msg":"繼「黑警還眼」後<br />\n901統一口號「黑警恐襲」「黑警放火」<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n出完貼要自推10下，見到其他都推下，回post都要post上面"},{"pid":"b70ae7a326684ac1e2da689c9480f49b68a25869","tid":1524530,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcf1572c953a86e2b3b3ec6b8924cbae1831a912","tid":1524530,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:15.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=be69d352\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=d76986fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=20696b3b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"6978888e0343c6f968969ab7564c926b37c2dfd2","tid":1524530,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都一樣，係無差別攻擊！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ef73fb61d847b9c2ae12bd15f60c90b147ebcad","tid":1524530,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8f2a5edacaf0a71f2c11343f7d97d7e7ca6c592","tid":1524530,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:33:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c7c7af93ac0dd6b0413e798d97fafdde7f152c1","tid":1524530,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f00a07be2e475ed083ba56cb494782a449b53c","tid":1524530,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:41:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ec0f5360031bc5b268f00aa0bff111d05920455e","tid":1524530,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:41:2